            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I'm aware that `nvim_open_win`, the corresponding floating window API, doesn't support that `window_opts` proposal for setting initial window options -- I threw it in since I think that's convenient, but if it's distracting from the core issue here, that's not the main point of this ticket (so it can be ignored or I can remove it). I'm not proposing that the two APIs should look meaningfully different from each other.",
